Oh yeah!
I did not notice that I've pushed my private repo on Github...

_Thanks for informing dude!_
I agree we actually use the Leaflet mapping library at work :)
I also agree on the same. Actually got this in my feed because was working on leaflet maps library from last couple of days..!!
I first thought a customized version of Leaflet(map library) is released

A popular templating engine called 'Jade' was forced to change their name to 'Pug' after some company claimed that they had the trademark of 'Jade'. This repo will get popular over time, so yeah.... We need a more marketable name.

Hey Guys,
Actually I got the "leaf logo" somehow on the internet...
And the name was just an trail to match the logo..
I agree with you guys and would like to know what name will be good for this project?
I am 15 year old and not so experienced in keeping names.
NOTE : This repo was previously known as "Pudding" but I had to change the name as I was not able to get a domain name
Thank you!

The activity feature is still a pending feature and I agree with you about the full stack error..
It is just for testing now...

Great work 😊 ....now a decent name ....Air? Breathe? I like breathe since it is simple and natural. Bee-social is also something that just popped into my head. Just spit balling here but well done regardless.

Cool names dude,
But l would like a name which goes with the leaf logo as well...
what about `sociaLeaf`?

It'll work...but I need
Something just out of the topic of Social media...
Something cute like Twitter.
I hope you get that.

Sprout
As in sprouting relationships or friendships etc. Then the leaf is still relevant.

Sprout is really nice..
We need to check if something like that already exists or not..
And then we can change the name!

Sprout is probably not a good name considering Sprout Social exists.

https://sproutsocial.com/
Maybe something like leaf-connect? I really like this repo by the way :)
You could go with smth more catsy but still containing the word leaf. For e.g 'Leafo'

This is not supposed to be an issue..
Please mail me instead of creating a issue.

My emailId is dj.srivastava23@gmail.com
Leafo will match to much results on google with other programming stuff because this is the most pupular scss compiler written in php: https://github.com/leafo/scssphp

Hey guys,
I got a name which is not used by any another company or project.
*Spruce* - It's a plant which has pine like leaves..
And it also sounds good!
ooh that sounds good and ``Spruce social`` will easily be on the top for google searches.

So should I change the name to `spruce`? 
Anyone with a better name?

Thanks to all for actively participating in the discussion!

Thanks for the basic structure...
Will soon work on the logical stuff after creating the Google Cloud Project.
Oh lol I was still working on it..
Spruce is great 👏👏 .. one more suggestion, not related to the name topic though but consider keeping a dark theme toggle ☺️
Spruce is good I'd change the logo though as a spruce tree has pine needles instead of deciduous leaves. Cheers.
[Here is an idea I had for the image](https://cdn.dancodes.online/Spruce-1)  but it isn't great

The error on your database is because.. You are using db.checkUser() instead of db.findOne()
I will correct that...

I think the image is pretty cool for now...
Will change the name to _Spruce_ soon.

Hey dude,
You should see utils/handlers/user.js
And see the difference between findOne() and checkUser().
I noticed that you change findOne() to checkUser() in your commits.

The correct one to use is findOne() in case of oauth sign-in. 
Check the website to see if there are multiple signins or not and then you'll check the difference.
